1:00:40.870 --> 1:00:43.000
Tidak banyak. Hanya satu.

1:00:43.070 --> 1:00:44.470
Soo juga di Seoul.

1:00:45.640 --> 1:00:48.040
Soo benar-benar memberinya keberuntungan.

1:00:48.940 --> 1:00:49.940
Benar juga.

1:00:52.710 --> 1:00:53.710
Apa?

1:00:54.610 --> 1:00:55.710
Apa?

