[Woo-yeon Kurang Ajar]

1:01:10.730 --> 1:01:11.730
Woo-yeon?

1:01:13.460 --> 1:01:14.470
Soo?

1:01:15.230 --> 1:01:16.370
Kenapa kau menjawab?

1:01:16.800 --> 1:01:18.840
Dia mencuci piring.
Haruskah kuberikan ponselnya?

1:01:19.400 --> 1:01:20.440
Tidak.

1:01:21.340 --> 1:01:24.810
